719600f-a.text:
East River Drive, at the foot of East 111th Street, showing a portion Jefferson Park which will form the west side of this new thoroughfare.
September 17, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.

719601f-b.text:
East River Drive, north of East 111th Street, showing on the left Jefferson Park extending northward to East 114th Street. This is a set
of 2 views; No. 2 of which shows the rivers edge.
July 16, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
